e organization default, and they can decide whether members can change naming in projects.","fileNamingConventionTooltip":"Set how your downloads are named across Creative Suite. Create custom naming templates, set defaults for your org or projects, and preview filenames before saving.","gptImage15":"\u003cstrong\u003eGPT Image 1.5\u003c/strong\u003e \u003climitedBadge tooltip='$t(pricingPlans:benefits:gptImage15Tooltip)' /\u003e","gptImage15Tooltip":"This model is unlimited until January 16, 2026.","gptImage2":"GPT Image 2","imageGenerationOnModelsLike":"\u003cstrong\u003eImage generation\u003c/strong\u003e on models like \u003cstrong\u003eNano Banana, \u003cnoBreak\u003eSeedream 4.5\u003c/noBreak\u003e, \u003cnoBreak\u003eFlux.2\u003c/noBreak\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ctooltip tooltip='$t(pricingPlans:benefits:imageGenerationOnModelsLikeTooltip)' /\u003e","imageGenerationOnModelsLikeTooltip":"Available on selected models: Seedream 4.5, Flux.2 Pro, Flux.2 Flex, Mystic 2.5, Google Nano Banana, Google Imagen 4, Reve, Z-Image, Ideogram 3, and Runway.","lowestCostPerCredit":"Lowest cost per credit","lowestCostPerCreditCheaper":"Lowest cost per credit \u003cbadge\u003e$t(pricingPlans:benefits:lowestCostPerCreditCheaperBadge)\u003c/badge\u003e","lowestCostPerCreditCheaperBadge":"20% CHEAPER","magnificAndTopazUpscalersBenefit":"Magnific \u0026 Topaz upscalers \u003ctooltip tooltip='$t(pricingPlans:benefits:magnificAndTopazUpscalersBenefitTooltip)' /\u003e","magnificAndTopazUpscalersBenefitTooltip":"High-quality AI upscaling for images and videos. Powered by Magnific and Topaz.","magnificImageAndVideoUpscalers":"Magnific image \u0026 video upscalers \u003ctooltip tooltip='$t(pricingPlans:benefits:magnificImageAndVideoUpscalersTooltip)' /\u003e","magnificImageAndVideoUpscalersTooltip":"High-quality AI upscaling for images and videos. Powered by Magnific.","magnificUpscaler":"Magnific upscalers \u003ctooltip tooltip='$t(pricingPlans:benefits:magnificUpscalerTooltip)' /\u